Package: cpu-tweaks
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libgtk-3-0, libglib2.0-0
Description: CPU frequency and power management GUI for Linux
 Native Linux GUI for CPU frequency, governor, turbo boost, and energy
 performance tuning. Supports Intel P-State, AMD P-State, and acpi-cpufreq
 drivers. Features live per-core frequency monitoring, drift detection,
 and privilege escalation via pkexec.
